description: Accessing your hard drives could never be easier with the Rosewill RX-DU101 docking station. This docking device allows you to exchange data stored on 2.5"/3.5" SATA HDD over USB 2.0 interface, without the hassle-of opening case and connecting cables. Hot-swap capability makes it great for multi-HDD use, while LED indicator gives intuitive status on power and activity. The USB 2.0 interface provides high bandwidth of up to 480 Mbps for fast data transfer. A conveniently placed Eject button allows quick HDD removal with a press of button.
title: Rosewill Plastic 2.5-Inch/3.5-Inch USB 2.0 Docking Station - Black (RX-DU101)
